``input_output_types``
 of 
``each``
 and 
``par-each``
 consistent
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11638] cleanup hide testing PR
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11622] removed cp-old
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11598] allowed math avg to work with durations
ysthakur 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11608] fixed a help menu regression
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11562] made it so we evaluate string interpolation at parse time
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11584] upgraded the byte-unit dependency
Tastaturtaste 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11535] improved navigation functionality through reedline
yukitomoda 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11590] implemented 
``<``
 and 
``>``
 operators for strings
NotLebedev 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11581] fixed explicit flags for plugins
andrei-27 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11580] added a new 
``--index``
 flag to 
``input list``
rsteube 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11442] added style support to the external completer
drbrain 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11322] added 
``into cell-path``
 for dynamic cell-path creation
stormasm updated versions (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11635] 1
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11594] 2
)
davehorner 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10558] fixed a panic caused by 
``ls \\.\pipe``
crides 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11636] fixed env conversion for buffer editor
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/11618] made it so that resolving external highlight takes the current PATH into account
